When working in this repository:

1. Read `AGENTS.md` at the repo root before starting any research task.
2. Follow `Deli_AutoResearch/SKILL.md` behavioral constraints: zero interaction, persist state to `tasks/<slug>/state/`, fresh session per iteration.
3. Route paper work via `Deli_AutoResearch/skills/router.md` and run `python tools/check_gates.py` between iterations.
4. Orchestrator ticks use `Deli_AutoResearch/orchestrator/loop_prompt.md`.
